{"tid":2239930,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇團隊證抗潰瘍藥可殺武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-10-12T10:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T03:10:26.000Z","uid":134071,"like":252,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"79b2538a4e3ddddab49d13f3a2cbdb4fb4fca363","tid":2239930,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:20:58.000Z","msg":"武漢疫情持續影響全球，科研界致力研發疫苗及藥物。港大化學系與港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇的團隊研究發現，一種常用抗潰瘍藥物「枸櫞酸鉍雷尼替丁」（Ranitidine Bismuth Citrate, RBC）在動物實驗中，證實有效抑制武肺病毒複製和紓緩與病毒相關的炎症，受感染倉鼠的鼻甲和肺部病毒載量下降10至100倍，與瑞德西韋效果相若，藥物毒性和價格亦較低，惟需待進一步臨床研究，才能知道應用在病人的理想時間和劑量，暫未知何時能進行後期臨床研究。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/AYKCWHXNBFGLRPHD4XDJO5464A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FAYKCWHXNBFGLRPHD4XDJO5464A%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBY26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=5894814c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FAYKCWHXNBFGLRPHD4XDJO5464A%2F&h=9659c2c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/AYKCWHXNBFGLRPHD4XDJO5464A/</a>"},{"pid":"eb0a739791f9259d0fcf200a860f65bdcc179c90","tid":2239930,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573774143311aea22ab45895d3e23d8d0d35e1ac","tid":2239930,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9bb48c158c60a6a91af5706d40d32371e2a267","tid":2239930,"uid":127575,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:24:39.000Z","msg":"違反國安法！拉得！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec37ca7b589a2e4c34e24d64f3c7fa6fe918b940","tid":2